man sachs in the energy and power industry he was cofounder and  cosenior managing director of carlyleriverstone global energy and power fund i lp carlyleriverstone global energy and power fund iii lp and carlyleriverstone global energy and power fund ii lp he has been cosenior managing director at riverstone holdings llc and riverstonecarlyle global energy and power fund iv lp since  he is responsible for sourcing and negotiating investments as well as postclosing portfolio company monitoring he serves as manager of enduro resource partners llc mr leuschen serves as the president at switchback ranch llc mr leuschen has extensive mergers and acquisitions financing and investing experience in the energy and power sector he served at the goldman sachs group inc mr leuschen spent  years with goldman sachs  co as a partner and a managing director he joined goldman sachs in  founded its global energy and power group in  served as its head since  and its partner from  to  mr leuschen was responsible for building the goldman sachs energy and power investment banking practice into one of the leading franchises in the global energy and power industry during this period he and his team participated in a large number of the major energy and power merger and acquisition transactions worldwide mr leuschen was responsible for establishing and managing goldman sachs relationships with senior executives from leading companies in all segments of the energy and power industry he served as managing director at the carlyle group lp where he focused on investments in energy and power sectors mr leuschen serves on the boards of directors of fieldwood energy llc venado canera resources titan operating legend natural gas ep energy enduro resource partners llc and enduro ii he has been a nonexecutive director of riverstone energy limited since may  he serves as a director buckeye pipe line company llc cambridge energy research associates j aron resources mega energy inc and natural meats mo